    "Background": {
      "text": "Also known as \"Surfer's eye\"\nBenign scleral growth\nMass of collagen degeneration and fibroblastic proliferation\nBegins near the medial canthus and grows laterally",
      "subsections": {
        "Risk_factors": {
          "text": "Sunlight (UV) exposure\nWindy, sandy and dusty environments\nMore common near the equator",
